TITLE: Episode 69 - The Vixens Meet Jeffrey Tucker
DESCRIPTION: This week, we nabbed a chat with Jeffrey Tucker to discuss his new book: Liberty or Lockdown. We talked about the economic and psychological damage wreaked by the government at every level over this last year and discussed what hopes we have for the future.
